{"tid":1577901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突破! 升級! 全面升級!] 變革要有嘅覺悟, 你準備好未?","createTime":"2019-09-18T02:17:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T16:30:24.000Z","uid":23830,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"064e3744a9015d196f87997e93cc1a2947b6b426","tid":1577901,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:17:44.000Z","msg":"重點長文，香港人必須一閱，找出個方向。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>社會變革要有嘅覺悟 【電影〈讓子彈飛〉的開示】</strong><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3pGUFHG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3pGUFHG.jpg&h=a0599b26&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n1.要對抗一個舊有以及既得利益者群體果陣，你要識咩係武力+政治權威嘅正當性。<br />\n<br />\n2.政治正當性都有對付唔到嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n3.當政治正當性唔夠用果陣，你就需要變化，武力呢個時候就派上用場。<br />\n<br />\n4.武力都會有解決唔到嘅問題，太多人不明所以迂腐根深蒂固，只會當你第二個權威嚟跪拜，這需要公民覺醒。<br />\n<br />\n5.文化+知識先係將公義社會理想延續落去嘅唯一方法。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">*6.呢個世界有太多毫不作為，助紂為虐嘅人，你要喺一個不公平嘅情境下去說服佢哋，根本就係唔可能，而且亦毫無意義，反而重會浪費自己嘅時間，甚至生命。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gONgT3v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgONgT3v.jpg&h=4b9270c8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">*7.要玩就要玩得贏。係一輸就萬劫不復嘅情境之下，每行一步都要深思熟慮，唔好俾情感衝昏頭腦，要控制自己嘅理智，仇一定要報，但唔急於一時。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yQfRHW0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyQfRHW0.jpg&h=3cb583b2&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n8.團隊入面每個人都會有自己嘅諗法，個個都會有自己想要嘅嘢，但最重要嘅就係紀律，要搵出真正清楚狀況嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iHJG5aw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiHJG5aw.jpg&h=d6cb9198&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">*9.社會變革呢條路係一定少人行，唔會有太多人理解你點解要做呢件事，佢哋都唔會想去理解，只要你贏，佢哋就會支持你</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">*10. 讓子彈飛=時間+製造將贏嘅感覺。<br />\n用一段時間引誘敵人出招連續出錯，暴露弱點搵方法對症下藥，要不斷製造贏嘅局勢，聲勢浩大，你要民眾支持你，必須要佢知道，你最後係會贏。</span></strong><br />\n <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GVc42Xn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGVc42Xn.jpg&h=7f3784c1&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"d9cf3835f711d41609070a8805016c13ea59f7bd","tid":1577901,"uid":23830,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:17:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>* 第六，第七，第九同第十最重要</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n以上4個覺悟要深入再講如下:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">關於第六：</span></strong><br />\n深藍，淺藍，花生友：示威者縱容暴徒破壞政府公物，破壞港鐵設施，警察暴力執法有理。但佢哋都忘記或刻意遺忘了事情嘅起因，只講結果。<br />\n佢哋講呢啲冇良心嘅嘢，原因係大家正正處身於一個不平公不公義嘅社會，佢哋只會遵從權貴無中生有顛倒黑白是非，唔會企在公道和公義呢一邊。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">政府用暴徒形容示威者，用暴動形容示威遊行，目的是打擊示威者想建立嘅公平宣言。</span></span></strong><br />\n咁多大好青年受到迫害自殺，被非禮被亂棍追打致腦出血骨折終身殘疾，被擊盲眼睛，甚至被拷打被殺死，就係因為示威者冒犯咗既港共嘅權威。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">731/831/卧底陷害/白衣人福建佬藍絲周街打人/警方濫捕不公平執法...根本冇人有辦法去解決呢啲明眼人都知道唔公平嘅情況。</span></strong></span><br />\n <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aNhs0KE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaNhs0KE.jpg&h=1fd0baf3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>關於第七 ：</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">要報仇就必須要玩得起，仲要玩得贏。</span></strong><br />\n方法：<br />\n1. 保護自己名聲重要; <br />\n2. 殺人誅心，即殺黃四郎之餘仲要令到其他人信服自己;<br />\n3. 要諗乜野可以令對方致命;要連根拔起，必須推翻黃四朗在百姓心目中牢不可破嘅地位。<br />\n4. 冷靜耐性佈署。<br />\n     真的革命者係知道打倒黃四朗係需要慢慢來，喺敵眾我寡之下， 魚死網破不但止報唔到仇， 仲有機會再失去自己的兄弟。<br />\n5. 決心，智慧嘅提升。<br />\n    喺一個輸就萬劫不復嘅情景之下，每行一步都要深思熟慮，唔好畀情感沖昏頭腦，要控制自己嘅你理智，仇係一定要報，但唔急於一時，覺悟&quot;玩得起&quot;嘅同時， 必需要同時有&quot;點樣玩得贏&quot;嘅覺悟。<br />\n <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4sjCDwF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4sjCDwF.jpg&h=81545616&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>關於第九： </strong></span><br />\n強權之所以好用是，你永遠不會贏...。<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>所謂中立派 ，睇定邊個贏先表態。更多嘅人，諗住都鬥唔過 ，咁就唯有做藍絲。而呢兩種人，你是冇辦法用公義嘅理由去動搖佢哋。<br />\n你要贏，係唔需要百姓支唔支持你。只要你贏，佢哋就會支持你。</strong></span><br />\n <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lty0BiE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLty0BiE.jpg&h=dec41884&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>關於第十：</strong></span><br />\n讓子彈飛=時間+製造將贏嘅感覺。<br />\n<br />\n用一段時間引誘敵人出招連續出錯，暴露弱點，呢樣嘢喺套戲入面就係花姐手上面黃四朗嘅替身，黃四朗嘅替身將係勝負關鍵，搵到佢你就會贏。<br />\n<br />\n不斷製造贏嘅局勢，聲勢浩大，你要人支持你，必須要佢知道，你最後係會贏。<br />\n<br />\n張木之用大量嘅彈子射向黃四朗嘅鐵門製造激戰嘅效果 ，呃偶爾偷睇形勢嘅民眾，如此民眾覺得乜打咁耐，這時用黃四朗替身一招偷天換日，所有人就會以為黃四朗今鋪仲唔死硬，咁即係張木之贏咗，於是好安心咁破除對權威嘅思想枷鎖，如此，黃四郎嘅權威就正式喺民眾心目中倒下。這時人民就會一批批大量衝出來革命了。<br />\n<br />\n可見人數其實唔係最重要方法先係最重要。喺呢度，唔係要有幾多人去衝，而係搵到推翻權威嘅方法，破除民眾嘅思想枷鎖，引起所有人都衝出去反抗。<br />\n<br />\n追求民意呀嗰啲都係嘥鬼氣，總之你贏到佢就會幫你就係咁簡單 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tWVybSy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtWVybSy.jpg&h=a97f0970&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">另外，最後社會變革完成後，還有一個覺悟：<br />\n社會變革之後，警醒自己唔好變成殺咗惡龍，但到最後貪婪變成另一條惡龍嘅勇者。</span></span></strong></em><br />\n<br />\n原意念出自:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/L6g4QOGqMBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL6g4QOGqMBY&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5JKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=5eb86f35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L6g4QOGqMBY</a>"},{"pid":"745d2135a59ef159c8d1b4acdf58615031015025","tid":1577901,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:18:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74ebe6ce8a7bc0ef052fd796833ad46c3c8e5c36","tid":1577901,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:23:53.000Z","msg":"簡單黎講需要同政府對等既武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f65577aadde97ba8068abac091c8aaed7783fd","tid":1577901,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:36:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"997960d508abf293c68b84c3774f81e047270056","tid":1577901,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:49:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bad9626d7c709a3a6f09ce17e6c77cb9edc435a0","tid":1577901,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:50:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"efd5e99582ac93e96a572dc3c3b4f58c73be1bc8","tid":1577901,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:41:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"adcf803d86766cd131fe525653364fcc026a7889","tid":1577901,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T02:25:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3315ea2bb1abec48eb2d71a1f71a6f093ed190be","tid":1577901,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T03:12:02.000Z","msg":"最後一句說話完全係講緊華盛頓<br />\n首先我哋要有一個咁醒的人帶領一隊人<br />\n其次...呢個運動的目標已唔再係林鄭政府...<br />\n變咗支共...敵人太大都唔係重點...<br />\n重點係太遠...<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170d2ee8c3b7a902ebc2734b095b7ef9eee775ef","tid":1577901,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T12:48:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4ca37b8aadb6c7fbae0bce375929cae29984eb3e","tid":1577901,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T23:04:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"306f793f390a938d737cc67d5349c0fcdaec623f","tid":1577901,"uid":102597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T23:24:11.000Z","msg":"齊齊變革者?"},{"pid":"ffa0e19dda31d27fc5d6aea892d737c0baa577b9","tid":1577901,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T02:02:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8809cb264b1f85cf44f8220a847693bf6a3b8095","tid":1577901,"uid":211034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T02:28:01.000Z","msg":"一齊去Twitter將 #929globalantichinazimarch <br />\n推上熱門 推到929全世界所有人都一齊standwithHK<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mjKZ7PA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmjKZ7PA.jpg&h=9c9f7bc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5sn1BHW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5sn1BHW.jpg&h=f59429dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/stjbYWh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FstjbYWh.jpg&h=231ca5f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QW0OgHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQW0OgHY.jpg&h=d6c222cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/opCg92Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FopCg92Z.jpg&h=5bd6bb90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a641b7c51a816ba04b3754ceafa958cf91594d90","tid":1577901,"uid":211034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T02:28:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a76f3d03623eaf1375d4faa6fa0f1ad067ba13b1","tid":1577901,"uid":326779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:30:24.000Z","msg":"要有贏果個勢，好同意 &ldquo;只要你個勢贏民意就會支持&rdquo; 既講法。多數人而家唔支持獨立，係因為佢地唔信可以做到，但只要佢地見將要成事，就會轉軚支持返"}]}